title: Old Bay Panko Shrimp and Roasted Zucchini with Sweet Potato Wedges and Lemon-Chive Dipping Sauce
description: Summer's here, and this delicious shrimp dinner will transport you to the shoreline for the evening! Our easy shake 'n' bake method gets crispy coated shrimp on the table in no time, so you can relax and enjoy the sunshine.
